Benfica are trying to take Arsenal's Joel Campbell on a loan or a permanent deal.

The Costa Rican is well down the striking pecking order and is open to leaving the Emirates Stadium.

Campbell was hugely impressive at the World Cup in Brazil and scored in the thrilling 3-1 victory over Uruguay.

